/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一開始咪講咗何君堯唔係Bar囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我只不過諗solic同bar雖然由兩個唔同組織管，但係專業失德呢啲條文應該係有common ground㗎嘛<br />\n我唔係讀law，所以我希望讀law嘅人睇吓有無位搵到入何君堯囉</blockquote><br />\n望下law soc council係咩人揸旗先啦<br />\n肯撚定何君堯唔會有事</blockquote><br />\n就算bar都一樣啦<br />\n睇下大眼雞肥婆 大舊石</blockquote><br />\n到依家仲有期望<br />\n<br />\n樓豬真係樂觀得可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下飯佔中好官搬龍門就知咩事啦"},{"pid":"9d09a9233f08d9fca9ab9669b64aac738487d3fe","tid":403732,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d08158a9694a0c3e2addbd982709affe70b6df6","tid":403732,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:47:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>CAP 200 CRIMES ORDINANCE</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><ins>Section 10 Offences</ins><br />\n<br />\n(1)Any person who&mdash;<br />\n(a)does or attempts to do, or makes any preparation to do, or conspires with any person to do, any act with a seditious intention; or<br />\n(b)utters any seditious words; or<br />\n(c)prints, publishes, sells, offers for sale, distributes, displays or reproduces any seditious publication; or<br />\n(d)imports any seditious publication, unless he has no reason to believe that it is seditious,<br />\nshall be guilty of an offence and shall be liable for a first offence to a fine of $5,000 and to imprisonment for 2 years, and for a subsequent offence to imprisonment for 3 years; and any seditious publication shall be forfeited to the Crown. (13 of 1938 s. 4 incorporated. Amended 22 of 1950 Schedule; 30 of 1970 s. 3)<br />\n<br />\n(2)Any person who without lawful excuse has in his possession any seditious publication shall be guilty of an offence and shall be liable for a first offence to a fine of $2,000 and to imprisonment for 1 year, and for a subsequent offence to imprisonment for 2 years; and such publication shall be forfeited to the Crown. (13 of 1938 s. 4 incorporated. Amended 22 of 1950 Schedule)<br />\n<br />\n(3)Where any person has been convicted of an offence under subsection (1) or (2) in respect of any seditious publication, the court may order the seizure and forfeiture of any copies of the seditious publication in the possession of&mdash;<br />\n(a)the person convicted; or<br />\n(b)any other person named in the order, if the court is satisfied by evidence on oath that the copies are in the possession of the other person for the use of the person convicted. (60 of 1971 s. 19 incorporated) [cf. 1819 c. 8 ss. 1 &amp; 2 U.K.]<br />\n<br />\n(4)Any copies seized under subsection (3) shall be disposed of as the court may direct; but no copies shall be destroyed until the expiration of the period within which an appeal may be lodged or, if an appeal is lodged, until the appeal has been finally determined or abandoned. (60 of 1971 s. 19 incorporated)<br />\n<br />\n(5)In this section&mdash;<br />\n&ldquo; seditious publication &rdquo; ( 煽動刊物 ) means a publication having a seditious intention;<br />\n&ldquo; seditious words &rdquo; ( 煽動文字 ) means words having a seditious intention. (13 of 1938 s. 2 incorporated)</em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f1a16b62fb2e5e2dbaab4037b27cc45e8f02358e","tid":403732,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e517f31a9eaf5a6ee2f08a471a9a37a24260f8e","tid":403732,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<br />\n希望釘埋佢律師牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"df6e8c031e7837bf60c62af316a8a6f9c1069217","tid":403732,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第212章 《侵害人身罪條例》<br />\n<br />\n5.串謀或唆使謀殺<br />\n<br />\n任何人在香港境內串謀、同謀及議同謀殺他人，以及在香港境內唆使、鼓勵、勸說、試圖勸說或建議別人謀殺他人，不論其謀殺對象屬何種國籍或具有何種公民身分或在任何地方，均屬犯罪，可處終身監禁。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>(由1911年第30號第2及5條修訂；由1983年第64號第4條修訂；由1999年第13號第3條修訂)<br />\n[比照 1861 c. 100 s. 4 U.K.]</strong></span>"},{"pid":"94dec54fb52a0d727c8b106e825c9033e97ea5a4","tid":403732,"uid":29649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9ce71c678cf67dd1d72209b47c12862743c293","tid":403732,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:21:06.000Z","msg":"睇埋仲有d咩台上講野既人。。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0141a741429170ad6eada321e04de54b11b97d3a","tid":403732,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇埋仲有d咩台上講野既人。。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"851d61bd654b79e6f4b4f0635c923e8f1ada18f9","tid":403732,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推爆佢條仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條撚樣真係好撚乞人憎<br />\n上網打句嘢都可以比人拉<br />\n咁都告唔鳩到佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地ㄧ定要佢付出代價"},{"pid":"44b94bf04048c53ad594a2ffc885e14941129167","tid":403732,"uid":5317